{"tid":811124,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【馬圈兩位Christine】一個陀住騎師BB現身！一個着小背心Show Quali","createTime":"2018-09-08T14:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T18:38:22.000Z","uid":8500,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"259382ee7a51e4d76eb5289ca136ce342bc9dca7","tid":811124,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"快活谷馬場這天(8日)舉行季內首次谷閘，多位馬主到場，包括「善傳千里」的鄭錦鐘博士、「請跟我來」的蔡漢秋、「瑰麗傳奇」的文壽強等，非常熱鬧。<br />\n一眾男士之外，這天在快活谷最矚目是有兩位都叫Christine的靚女現身，一個是騎師蔡明紹太太衛文娟Christine，她懷有身孕近8個月，預產期11月初，今胎是BB仔，今早Christine腹大便便到場，和女兒Jessica May及蔡明紹形影不離，一家人享受家庭樂，非常溫馨。<br />\n另一位Christine是「日日精彩」馬主王家揚太太。Christine笑容燦爛，向有馬圈女神之稱，她這天身穿粉紅色窄身運動背心到場，豐滿身形表露無遺，她小鳥依人般孖住新婚丈夫一齊睇「日日精彩」試閘，而這匹未曾出賽的灰馬，結果在郭能胯下試閘跑第五，不過不失。不過Christine看來仍心情大靚，似乎頗滿意愛駒進度。<br />\n除了「日日精彩」，王家揚有匹「帶榮來」列陣周日(9日)沙田第五場四班1200米草地賽，究竟機會如何呢？王家揚說：「『帶榮來』季內首次上陣，部署由練馬師姚本輝揸主意，希望有好表現啦，牠上季尾最後一戰因天雨影響發揮，形勢不太有利，但我們對此駒仍有一定的信心。」<br />\n王家揚大哥王文揚則透露，他們兩兄弟會在賽日帶同另一半入馬場，為愛駒打氣，希望「帶榮來」會有好表現。  <br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180908&amp;s=10860680&amp;a=58658678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180908%26s%3D10860680%26a%3D58658678&d=X6rhx2bzFlrsuPJ%2BUbrbMpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f08afa9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180908%26s%3D10860680%26a%3D58658678&h=58bc360b\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180908&amp;s=10860680&amp;a=58658678</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180908/large/1536376790_f611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180908%2Flarge%2F1536376790_f611.jpg&h=96e9e7e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180908/large/1536376790_8f7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180908%2Flarge%2F1536376790_8f7c.jpg&h=612c1ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180908/large/1536376795_bc8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180908%2Flarge%2F1536376795_bc8b.jpg&h=1328280a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180908/large/1536376795_0b4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180908%2Flarge%2F1536376795_0b4f.jpg&h=be46da3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0461ff16aa371fec51fbed7b3d8713a70856e707","tid":811124,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b5f632c0dd5a8f35a35df458528961ecaafa4f4","tid":811124,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85867f2c034064a3d6953c164bd58295a2f15215","tid":811124,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:26:17.000Z","msg":"馬上全接觸"},{"pid":"ca4f5d381c5acf261dbd4e8720b9c3cff8a83a1c","tid":811124,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T18:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}